<p>December 23, 2015</p>
<blockquote><p>The county also received a boost last month when a federal judge lifted a similar injunction against Forsyth County, N.C.</p>
<p>The Forsyth case was a cornerstone of the American Civil Liberties Union’s argument in seeking an injunction against the Pittsylvania County Board of Supervisors.</p></blockquote>
